            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Combine the<strong> beef</strong> <strong>mince </strong>and <strong>lemon zest </strong>in a bowl with <strong>half </strong>the <strong>grated</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), the <strong>ground</strong> <strong>coriander</strong>, <strong>half</strong> the <strong>ground</strong> <strong>cumin</strong>, <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>mint</strong> (save the rest for later!)<strong> </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until thoroughly combined (clean hands are the best way!) and shape into 6 <span class=\"text-danger\">[12] </span><strong>meatballs</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
