    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>meatballs</strong> and cook for 2 min on each side or until browned</p><p>Once the meatballs have browned, transfer them to a plate and set aside, (these will finish cooking in the sauce later)</p>",
